ri,sans-serif\">Any city tour, Monument entry etc</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">They also offer following optional services on request and will be charged accordingly:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Transportation from Delhi/Chandigarh to Shimla.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Paragliding</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Skiing</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Barbeque</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Corporate Setup</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Day tour of Shimla, Kufri &amp; Fagu</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Premium Alcohol</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">One bottle of mineral water per person per day</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Bonfire on party day</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-rig