 coupled by the feat of <em>Mallakhamb</em> on Indian Pole. Also, there will be a splendid display of fireworks along with the acro-bike performance. Don&rsquo;t forget to capture the moments of duo-trapeze performance, which symbolize trust and synchronicity. It&rsquo;s going to be a performance that you will remember for the lifetime.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>The event is happening in New Delhi from 25 December 2018 to 6 January 2019 at GMR Aerocity.</strong> The performance will be of two-hour duration and is available for time slots &ndash; 1 PM &amp; 5 PM every day. Choose the day and time of your convenience and be at the venue to experience the 43<sup>rd</sup> production by Cirque du Soleil, the global theatrical leader.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Top-notch acrobats, fascinating characters and impressive choreographic performances await you! Book your tickets now to indulge in a lifetime experience of entertainment combined with ambition, precision, balance, emotion </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">and</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> positive energy. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Seats are filling fast! <strong>Book your tickets now.</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Starting Price for a ticket: Rs 1500. </strong>To buy tickets click on the <strong>&quot;Official ticket URL&quot;</strong> button<strong>.</strong></span></span></p>','2018-12-25','2019-01-06','13:00:00','17:00:00','15