 cherished for a lifetime. &nbsp;<span style=\"color:#333333\"><strong>Now, it&rsquo;s your turn to explore yourself into the exciting extravaganza, which continues for about three days in the middle of historical forts, ancient haveli, Jain temples, majestic palaces, and indigenous culture as well.</strong> </span>Romantic, remote and unspoiled, the location comes to life during the extravaganza of the delights of the desert. The immense desert offers more than one can expect, so enjoy the privilege of laying in the sand with bright illuminating stars overhead and the desert silence ready to engulf you. Catch a glimpse of the local culture, tradition with the folk songs and dances to amuse and entertain you.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u>Date</u></strong>:<strong> </strong>29th December 2018 to 2nd January 2019</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u>Pickup</u></strong>: Dhola Kuan Metro Station / Iffco Chowk, Gurgaon at 8.00 pm on 29th December 2018.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u>Itinerary </u></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><strong>29th Dec 2018 (Day 1)</strong></em>: Departure From Delhi - Depart from Delhi for Jaisalmer.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><strong>30th Dec 2018 (Day 2)</strong></em>: Jaisalmer Sightseeing- Arrival Jaisalmer in the afternoon and check in at the hotel. After&nbsp;resting