ime: 5:30 am</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>5 KM Run</strong>: Participants need to be at least 8 Years old&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>10.5 KM Run</strong>: Participants need to be at least 12 Years old</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>21.1 KM Run</strong>: Participants need to be at least 15 Years old</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">*Top 3 Runners (in Male &amp; Female Categories respectively) will Get Gifts &amp; Awards!</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>','2019-01-27','2019-01-27','05:30:00','09:30:00','1542990778.jpg','1542990778.jpg',24,'','https://www.justplaysportz.com/event/ncr-half-marathon-2nd-edition','https://www.justplaysportz.com/event/ncr-half-marathon-2nd-edition','https://www.facebook.com/festevemantra/','https://twitter.com/festevemantra','','','','','',0,49,1,1,2,0,1,1,'2018-11-23 23:32:58','2018-11-24 00:01:38'),(38,'New Year Celebration: Pawna Lakeside Camping','new-year-pawana-lakeside-Camping',4,0,'<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Celebrate the New Year in Pawna Lakeside and ring in the year 2019 with great music, awesome food....</span></span></p>','<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Celebrate the <strong>New Year in Pawna Lakeside</strong> and ring in the year 2019 with great music, awesome food, and a wonderful bonfire experience. Pawna Lake is located in Maval Taluka of Pawna district and is a serene camping side. Not just the New Year but the first day of the year 2019 will be equally beautiful, as you will wake up to the delightful Pawna Lake. Party hard all night, and relax during the daytime with a picturesque lakeside view. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Not just the Lake, but there are many other tourist attractions nearby to make your New Year plan with your loved ones memorable. You can walk through the memory lane and indulge in the splendors of the Indian History while taking a stroll at Tikona, Tung, Lohgad and Visapur fort. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><em>Who Can Be a Part of This Event?</em></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Anyone who enjoy Camping and Bonfire beside Lake, and find good food just irresistible.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><em>Itinerary:</em></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Day Welcome to our Campsite1 :&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Try reaching our <strong>Campsite by 4 pm</strong> (Conveyance to the campsite is not included in the package). You will get your own tents, where you can freshen up, unpack your bags and settle down as many exciting activities are lined up.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Evening Snacks/ Refreshments</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Around <strong>5: 30 pm, evening snacks, and hot tea</strong> will be served in our dining area. Enjoy the sunset while having refreshments and explore the campsite. Or, you can just sit by the lakeside and enjoy the whispering sound waves.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Bonfire &amp; Party Time </strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Around 8 pm, the <strong>Bonfire Session will start with a bang! Loud music and DJ </strong>will help you let loose yourself. No one is judging your dance steps, so just dance your heart out and enjoy the New Year party.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Dinner Time</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=