 time with those who are craving for your love and attention.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">At the event, there will be many exciting activities like games and rides. Those who are looking for some fun time with pet animals can come at off-leash zones and indulge in a wonderful experience. In this area, you can find <strong>doggy ball pools</strong>, <strong>trampolines</strong>, <strong>tunnels</strong>, <strong>hurdles</strong>, <strong>Have-A-Go Agility</strong> and<strong> various fun games</strong>. Don&rsquo;t forget to take your pet to the Temptation Alley, where your dog will be tempted by treats like food and toys while you are trying to call him/ her back to you. If your pet succeeds in resisting the temptation, he/ she will win the round and get an exciting gift hamper!</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Other exciting activities are lined up at the <strong>Pet Fed 2018</strong>, <strong>such as fashion show for pets with Dino Morea and security dog show.</strong> There is also a dedicated cat zone for your feline friend, where she can enjoy exclusive games. And, there will be the aqua world, which will take you to the ecosphere that bleeds blue.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">There will be more than <strong>100 stalls</strong> for your pet at the event. So, get ready to enjoy a memorable stroll with your pet all across the event location. The more you explore the place, the higher are your chances of discovering something awesome. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">We know, the more is merrier! If you want to bring a new furry into your family, adoption camps are just for you. There you can discover dogs of over <strong>50 breeds </strong>(including our desi ones). Don&rsquo;t forget to be there at the time of <strong>Pet Fed Awards</strong>, which aim to honour some amazing work in the pet care industry. You can also vote online in categories like <strong>Best Debut Award- 2018</strong>, <strong>Doggie Baker &amp; Chef Award - 2018, Glamorous Groomer Award- 2018</strong> and <strong>Veterinarian Award- 2018</strong>. Remember, every vote count!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Book online to get amazing discounts! -&nbsp;Click on the &quot;<strong>Official Ticket URL</strong>&quot; button.</span></p>','2018-12-15','2018-12-16','11:00:00','21:00:00','1543428592.jpg','1543428592.jpg',30,'','http://delhi.petfed.org/','http://petfed.org/','https://www.facebook.com/petfedindia/','https://twitter.com/petfedindia','','https://www.instagram.com/petfedindia/','','https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXCUKRYHbplagxYM_MTukag','',0,162,1,1,2,0,1,1,'2018-11-29 01:09:52','2018-12-02 15:46:33'),(43,'UltraViolet Music Festival - New Year Eve 2018','ultraviolet-music-festival-new-year-eve-2018',1,0,'<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The fifth edition of UltraViolet Music Festival is finally happening! People of Ahmedabad need to get ....</span></span></p>','<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The fifth edition of <strong>UltraViolet Music Festival</strong> is finally happening! People of Ahmedabad need to get ready to groove. Mesmerizing feats of Bollywood and international acts and a lot more are going to happen under the starts in Ahmedabad for the first time. So, <strong>block your dates for the New Year