\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Celebrity chefs, live music and a lot more. The Palate Fest is what you were looking for so many days! Groove to the tunes of your </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">favourite</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> music artists while your plate is filled with lip-smacking dishes. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Remember that the entry to the Fest is </span></span><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Free!</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> Be ready for an all-encompassing Food &amp; Music Festival loved by families and youth alike. This gastronomic adventure will bring together a wide range of chefs and cooking sessions to treat you to a culinary experience&nbsp;like never before.</span></span></p>','2018-12-14','2018-12-16','11:30:00','22:30:00','1544256119.jpg','1544256119.jpg',40,'','http://www.palatefest.com/','http://www.palatefest.com/','https://www.facebook.com/htpalatefest/','https://twitter.com/PalateFest?lang=en','','https://www.instagram.com/htpalatefest/','','','',0,71,1,0,2,0,1,1,'2018-12-08 15:01:59','2018-12-08 15:56:21');
